row.header: Lists of films by letter & number

bdy.p: This group of articles compose a list in alphabetical order of films with articles in Wikipedia or a significant section in another article (such as a novel's article).

In the beginning of film titles, ignore all articles ("a", "an", "the", "le", "la", "les", "der", "die", "das", "il", "gli", "el", etc.), unless the entire title of the film consists only of those articles, or the word, as used in the title, is not an article, e.g. the word 'Die' in Die Hard would only be an article if the movie had been in German. In the rest of the title, ignore additionally such words as: "and", "&", "in", "of". If such words are included, use the next word in the title for sorting.
For guidelines on adding new entries, see the Talk page. Also, please, note that the list is not automatically updated.
